  <brief_title>Safety of LBH589 Alone and in Combination With Intravenous Docetaxel and Prednisone</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase IA/IB, Two Arm, Multi-center, Open-label, Dose Escalation Study of Oral LBH589 Alone and in Combination With IV Docetaxel and Oral Prednisone in Hormone Refractory Prostate Cancer (HRPC)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
